reviewText: This collection brings back childhood memories of clean movies for children.
What the heck? I thought I was ordering Disney movies, but instead received amateur theater productions!!! I put it in the trash, I was so disappointed.
Great kids musical fairy tale movies
We like the real people fairy tales, these were well done in my estimation, good quality, and a bargain for 3 in one.
Movies are pretty cheesy watching them back 20 years later, but they are classic and bring back great memories!
What a wonderful dvd it has three great classics on it and would recommend it to anyone who loves old stories
This is an excellent children's DVD it has three stories all very old fairy tales I would recommend this to anyone
